data.name: fbxCommon.InputSQL
data.value: SELECT '%', FN_ADM_MSG('221') FROM DUAL UNION ALL SELECT A.GWA,A.GWA_NAME FROM VW_BAS_GWA A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.OUT_JUNDAL_PART_YN = 'Y' AND FN_BAS_LOAD_VW_BAS_GWA_YMD(A.GWA, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE ORDER BY 1

data.name: cbxOrderGubun.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '%' , FN_ADM_MSG('221') FROM DUAL UNION SELECT A.CODE , A.CODE_NAME FROM OCS0132 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.CODE_TYPE = 'ORDER_GUBUN_BAS' ORDER BY 1
